# Dynamic Context Discovery

**Core Rule:** Reference files, don't load them. Agent discovers files only when needed.

---

## ✅ DO: Reference Files

```markdown
## Recent Work
- Feature: `prompts/dashboard/27-user-profile.md`
- Task: `prompts/tasks/01-list-prompts.md`
```

**Why:** Agent loads files only when needed, not on every message.

---

## ❌ DON'T: Copy Content

```markdown
## Recent Work
[Pastes entire 500-line prompt here]  ❌
```

**Why:** Bloats context with unused content.

---

## Patterns

### Summaries
- Reference: `path/to/file.md` (description)
- Never paste full content

### File Names
- Use: `27-feature-name.md` (number + clear name)
- Avoid: `feature.md` (too generic)

### Organization
- Group by domain: `prompts/dashboard/`, `prompts/wizard/`
- Create index files for large directories

---

## Quick Reference

**Summary format:**
```markdown
# Title
## Section
- Item: `path/to/file.md` (status)
```

**File naming:**
- Format: `##-feature-name.md`
- Examples: `27-user-profile.md`, `28-company-profile.md`

---

**Result:** ~47% token reduction, better focus, faster responses.
